title: The Portrend Trendblazers 11/25: Thanksgiving Food, Clifford, Maradona, Dan Rather, Nick Saban
itunes:title: The Portrend Trendblazers 11/25: Thanksgiving Food, Clifford, Maradona, Dan Rather, Nick Saban
description:
On this edition of The Portrend Trendblazers Jack and Miles discuss the food we're all eating for Thanksgiving, the first looks at live-action Clifford the Big Red Dog, Argentine Soccer legend Maradona has passed away, Dan Rather appears drunk, and Nick Saban tests positive for COVID.
